
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login - CDF Entrenamiento Elite</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design-system.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .login-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 3rem;
        }

        .login-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo-container {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 80px;
            width: auto;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .login-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }

        .login-subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .form-label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        .form-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .form-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #667eea;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .input-icon {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-icon i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 1rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: #9ca3af;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .input-icon .form-input {
            padding-left: 3rem;
        }

        .login-button {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .login-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }

        .login-button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .alert {
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .alert-error {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            color: #dc2626;
        }

        .alert-success {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            color: #16a34a;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        .footer-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .footer-logo img {
            height: 32px;
            width: auto;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .login-container {
                padding: 1rem;
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .login-card {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .login-title {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
            }

            .footer-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }
        }

        .system-info {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .system-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .credentials {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 0.75rem 0;
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-card">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/FQJBs2g/unnamed-2.png" alt="CDF Elite Logo" class="logo" 
                     onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='/images/cdf-logo-final.png';">
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="login-title">Bienvenido</h1>
            <p class="login-subtitle">Sistema de Gestión CDF Entrenamiento Elite</p>

            <!-- Flash Messages -->
            <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-error">
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
                    <%= error %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            <% if (typeof success !== 'undefined' && success) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-success">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                    <%= success %>
                </div>
            <% } %>

            <form method="POST" action="/login">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="username" class="form-label">Usuario</label>
                    <div class="input-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                        <input type="text" id="username" name="username" class="form-input" 
                               placeholder="Ingrese su usuario" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password" class="form-label">Contraseña</label>
                    <div class="input-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" class="form-input" 
                               placeholder="Ingrese su contraseña" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="login-button">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i>
                    Iniciar Sesión
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="system-info">
            <h3>Sistema de Gestión CDF Elite</h3>
            <p>Plataforma integral para la administración de gimnasios y centros de entrenamiento.</p>
            <div class="credentials">
                <strong>Usuario:</strong> administrador<br>
                <strong>Contraseña:</strong> CDFElite2025**
            </div>
            <p><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Sistema seguro y confiable</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-text">© 2025 CDF Entrenamiento Elite</div>
            <a href="#" class="footer-logo">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/9kcT37yD/unnamed-1.png" alt="CDF Logo" 
                     onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='/images/cdf-logo-final.png';">
            </a>
            <div class="footer-text">Desarrollado por Alan Stefanov, Software Engineer.</div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
